{"type":"answer","id":281385,"parentType":"question","parentId":26249,"uid":14173,"contents":"最近我的一个反贼朋友也把这个拿来质问我，还问我“你看的自由媒体有没有把这个公布出来让你们看”，还说我给他发的”Do You Hear the Hong Kong People Sing- 問誰未發聲““听起来是讽刺”。我一开始也是懵了，以为是大陆人冒充的，但他拿出了官网图片，说是有183万市民参加街站签名<a href=\"https://cdn.signforhk2020.com/signforhk2020.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.signforhk2020.com/signforhk2020.jpg</a><br>\n我稍微去官网看了一下，发现活动是在5月24日至31日搞的，本来想试试网上签名，但签不了。<br>\n这是官网<a href=\"https://cdn.signforhk2020.com/posts/images/2020/05/26/4_20200526_084700_UmJoxO.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.signforhk2020.com</a>活动回顾里给出的图片<br>\n<a href=\"https://cdn.signforhk2020.com/posts/images/2020/05/26/4_20200526_084700_UmJoxO.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.signforhk2020.com/posts/images/2020/05/26/4_20200526_084700_UmJoxO.jpg</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://cdn.signforhk2020.com/posts/images/2020/05/26/4_20200526_084902_QEHKX5.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.signforhk2020.com/posts/images/2020/05/26/4_20200526_084902_QEHKX5.jpg</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://cdn.signforhk2020.com/posts/images/2020/05/26/4_20200526_084931_RjIZJb.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.signforhk2020.com/posts/images/2020/05/26/4_20200526_084931_RjIZJb.jpg</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://cdn.signforhk2020.com/posts/images/2020/05/26/4_20200526_084955_ocVWCu.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.signforhk2020.com/posts/images/2020/05/26/4_20200526_084955_ocVWCu.jpg</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://cdn.signforhk2020.com/posts/images/2020/05/26/4_20200526_084325_4bH4bj.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.signforhk2020.com/posts/images/2020/05/26/4_20200526_084325_4bH4bj.jpg</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://cdn.signforhk2020.com/posts/images/2020/05/26/4_20200526_084419_jrP98M.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.signforhk2020.com/posts/images/2020/05/26/4_20200526_084419_jrP98M.jpg</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://cdn.signforhk2020.com/posts/images/2020/05/27/4_20200527_105032_psWhJc.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.signforhk2020.com/posts/images/2020/05/27/4_20200527_105032_psWhJc.jpg</a><br>\n我就特别选几张人数看起来比较多的放在这好了，剩下的大家可以去官网看。<br>\n我只能说，这是什么？“不要随地吐痰，要爱护环境”的小区公益宣传吗 ？靠着几张做作的图片就能证明有百万人签名了？呵呵，那你是没见过香港69游行，616游行的图片。<br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e4/June9protestTreefong03.jpg/600px-June9protestTreefong03.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e4/June9protestTreefong03.jpg/600px-June9protestTreefong03.jpg\" alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e4/June9protestTreefong03.jpg/600px-June9protestTreefong03.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n从金钟<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%BB%8D%E5%99%A8%E5%BB%A0%E8%A1%97\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">军器厂街</a>望向<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%BB%92%E5%B0%BC%E8%A9%A9%E9%81%93\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">轩尼诗道</a>的示威人潮<br>\n<br>\n人潮需用上7条行车线及两旁人行道<br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/ab/Demonstration_in_Yee_Wo_Street_20190609.jpg/608px-Demonstration_in_Yee_Wo_Street_20190609.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/ab/Demonstration_in_Yee_Wo_Street_20190609.jpg/608px-Demonstration_in_Yee_Wo_Street_20190609.jpg\" alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/ab/Demonstration_in_Yee_Wo_Street_20190609.jpg/608px-Demonstration_in_Yee_Wo_Street_20190609.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n铜锣湾<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%80%A1%E5%92%8C%E8%A1%97\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">怡和街</a>的游行情景<br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/59/Foo_Tak_Building【警告：链接内容可能存在钓鱼网址，请勿打开】_Banner_20190609-combin e.jpg/1081px-Foo_Tak_Building_Banner_20190609-combine.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/59/Foo_Tak_Building【警告：链接内容可能存在钓鱼网址，请勿打开】_Banner_20190609-combin e.jpg/1081px-Foo_Tak_Building【警告：链接内容可能存在钓鱼网址，请勿打开】_Banner_20190609-combin e.jpg\" alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/59/Foo_Tak_Building【警告：链接内容可能存在钓鱼网址，请勿打开】_Banner_20190609-combin e.jpg/1081px-Foo_Tak_Building_Banner_20190609-combine.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n湾仔富德楼外墙展示的标语直幡<br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/83/June9protestTreefong02.jpg/1200px-June9protestTreefong02.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/83/June9protestTreefong02.jpg/1200px-June9protestTreefong02.jpg\" alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/83/June9protestTreefong02.jpg/1200px-June9protestTreefong02.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<ul><li>湾仔<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%BB%92%E5%B0%BC%E8%A9%A9%E9%81%93\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">轩尼诗道</a>人山人海的游行情景</li></ul><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/57/Demonstration_in_Queensway_20190609.jpg/608px-Demonstration_in_Queensway_20190609.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/57/Demonstration_in_Queensway_20190609.jpg/608px-Demonstration_in_Queensway_20190609.jpg\" alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/57/Demonstration_in_Queensway_20190609.jpg/608px-Demonstration_in_Queensway_20190609.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%87%91%E9%90%98%E9%81%93\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">金钟道</a>傍晚一度下雨，游行人士举起雨伞，犹如2014年的“<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%9B%A8%E5%82%98%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">雨伞运动</a>”<br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/eb/Demonstration_in_Legislative_Council_Road_20190609.jpg/1200px-Demonstration_in_Legislative_Council_Road_20190609.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/eb/Demonstration_in_Legislative_Council_Road_20190609.jpg/1200px-Demonstration_in_Legislative_Council_Road_20190609.jpg\" alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/eb/Demonstration_in_Legislative_Council_Road_20190609.jpg/1200px-Demonstration_in_Legislative_Council_Road_20190609.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n晚上7时，民阵在立法会道举行集会<br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8d/June9protestTreefong06.jpg/1200px-June9protestTreefong06.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8d/June9protestTreefong06.jpg/1200px-June9protestTreefong06.jpg\" alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8d/June9protestTreefong06.jpg/1200px-June9protestTreefong06.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n晚上8时，未完成游行的市民与警方对峙<br>\n<br>\n到晚上9时，警方出动多辆运员车等警车戒备，而后方港铁<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%87%91%E9%90%98%E7%AB%99\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">金钟站</a>B出口仍逼满离开的游行人士<br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/47/June9protestTreefong09.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/47/June9protestTreefong09.jpg\" alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/47/June9protestTreefong09.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n晚上9时，警方出动<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E6%88%B0%E8%A1%93%E5%B0%8F%E9%9A%8A\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">特别战术小队</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4c/Demosist%C5%8D_protest_in_Legestive_Council_car_entrance_20190609.jpg/1200px-Demosist%C5%8D_protest_in_Legestive_Council_car_entrance_20190609.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4c/Demosist%C5%8D_protest_in_Legestive_Council_car_entrance_20190609.jpg/1200px-Demosist%C5%8D_protest_in_Legestive_Council_car_entrance_20190609.jpg\" alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4c/Demosist%C5%8D_protest_in_Legestive_Council_car_entrance_20190609.jpg/1200px-Demosist%C5%8D_protest_in_Legestive_Council_car_entrance_20190609.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>夜晚8时33分，<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">香港众志</a>成员在立法会停车场外静坐，要求在12号前见保安局局长<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%B6%E8%B6%85\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">李家超</a>及行政长官<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">林郑月娥</a>。警察于翌晨约2时半逐一抬走静坐者<br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/35/June16protestTreefong16.jpg/600px-June16protestTreefong16.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/35/June16protestTreefong16.jpg/600px-June16protestTreefong16.jpg\" alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/35/June16protestTreefong16.jpg/600px-June16protestTreefong16.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n下午7时，游行人士途径湾仔<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%BB%92%E5%B0%BC%E8%A9%A9%E9%81%93\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">轩尼诗道</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/c/ce/Hong_Kong_Demonstration_20190616_Victoria_Park-1.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/c/ce/Hong_Kong_Demonstration_20190616_Victoria_Park-1.jpg\" alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/c/ce/Hong_Kong_Demonstration_20190616_Victoria_Park-1.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n下午2时43分，民阵从<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%B6%AD%E5%A4%9A%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9E%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">维多利亚公园</a>出发<br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/99/190616_HK_Protest_Incendo_03.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/99/190616_HK_Protest_Incendo_03.jpg\" alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/99/190616_HK_Protest_Incendo_03.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n下午5时，刚刚出发的民众占满整条<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%AB%98%E5%A3%AB%E5%A8%81%E9%81%93\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">高士威道</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/ad/Protesters_occupy_Harcourt_Road_aerial_view_20190616.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/ad/Protesters_occupy_Harcourt_Road_aerial_view_20190616.jpg\" alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/ad/Protesters_occupy_Harcourt_Road_aerial_view_20190616.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n到傍晚6时40分，游行人士再次占领<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A4%8F%E6%85%A4%E9%81%93\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">夏悫道</a>所有行车线<br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/c/c0/190616_HK_Protest_Incendo_21.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/c/c0/190616_HK_Protest_Incendo_21.jpg\" alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/c/c0/190616_HK_Protest_Incendo_21.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n晚上10时，仍有大批民众留守<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A4%8F%E6%85%A4%E9%81%93\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">夏悫道</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/7/73/Hong_Kong_Station_to_Central_Station_Access_overcrowded_20190616.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/7/73/Hong_Kong_Station_to_Central_Station_Access_overcrowded_20190616.jpg\" alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/7/73/Hong_Kong_Station_to_Central_Station_Access_overcrowded_20190616.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n由<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%AB%99\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">香港站</a>往<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0%E7%AB%99\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">中环站</a>准备前往游行的人潮<br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/80/Hong_Kong_Demonstration_20190616_Causeway_Bay-1.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/80/Hong_Kong_Demonstration_20190616_Causeway_Bay-1.jpg\" alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/80/Hong_Kong_Demonstration_20190616_Causeway_Bay-1.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n铜锣湾<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%BB%92%E5%B0%BC%E8%A9%A9%E9%81%93\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">轩尼诗道</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B8%8C%E6%85%8E%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">希慎广场</a>外<br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/6b/190616_HK_Protest_Incendo_16.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/6b/190616_HK_Protest_Incendo_16.jpg\" alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/6b/190616_HK_Protest_Incendo_16.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%87%91%E9%90%98%E9%81%93\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">金钟道</a><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A4%AA%E5%8F%A4%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">太古广场</a>外<br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/98/Sea_of_protesters_giving_way_to_buses_to_leave_Harcourt_Road_20190616.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/98/Sea_of_protesters_giving_way_to_buses_to_leave_Harcourt_Road_20190616.jpg\" alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/98/Sea_of_protesters_giving_way_to_buses_to_leave_Harcourt_Road_20190616.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/5e/June16protestTreefong20.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/5e/June16protestTreefong20.jpg\" alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/5e/June16protestTreefong20.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/9e/190616_HK_Protest_Incendo_17.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/9e/190616_HK_Protest_Incendo_17.jpg\" alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/9e/190616_HK_Protest_Incendo_17.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<b>游行人士让路景象</b><br>\n<b>此举被称为香港版“摩西分红海”，被称赞为展现香港人的优秀游行秩序</b><br>\n<br>\n这才叫百万人，这才叫游行，这才叫民意！谁真谁假一目了然。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n就算69，616是警方说的24万，33.8万，那大家想想签名的183万是什么概念，为什么官方不把图片人数拍的更多点，要知道示威游行已经是上升到实际行动中了，而签名的话大笔一挥，用脚想想肯定是签名人数多，你说是183人然后翻几番我倒信。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n更多的图片大家自己找吧，只能说土共就是土共，那股深入到骨子里的“土”味是永远改不了的。","date":"2020-06-03","agreeCount":4,"discussionCount":0}